column5:
78 pages, Invited contribution, Plasma Physics of gamma ray emission
  from pulsars and their nebulae, Journal of Plasma Physics. arXiv admin note:
  text overlap with arXiv:1603.05731

column6:
JETP Letters (Russian edition), vol. 108 (2018), issue 1, page 5;
  Jetp Lett. (2018). https://doi.org/10.1134/S0021364018130015 (English
  edidtion)

column5:
More specific details on non-Hamiltonian achievements in modern time;
  a new subsection on extended Hadamard regularization; new results from
  effective field theory; some references upgraded, corrected, and added;
  corrected misprints in Eq. (6.12). The modifications relate to G.Sch\"afer &
  P.Jaranowski, Living Rev Relativ (2018) 21: 7; they will be included in the
  next update of the LRR article
